{"tid":1778071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我相信香港民主運動最後一道障礙係對法治嘅遵從","createTime":"2019-12-10T16:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:35:57.000Z","uid":235588,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4d6b8c1177cda79bcb646fe7aeb8e4551a3a9e","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"香港人喺呢半年入面改變咗好多，包括和勇合一，做到手段上嘅統一，但概嘆當見住咁多手足身陷牢獄，但香港人嘅困境係諗住「點喺法律制度下幫助手足」。呢點係務實，但我會反思呢班手足應否被判刑，佢地係咪有罪之身？正如孫中山如果起義失敗，被大清起訴佢有罪，咁佢應唔應該有罪？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我無資格判斷呢種對法治遵從是好是壞，因為起碼呢刻我都係被社會壓迫成為一個要守法嘅公民。但係我悲嘆呢幾千個被捕嘅手足不值背負一個不相稱嘅罪責，什至不應有罪。然而香港人起碼在呢刻仲妥協於現時法律框架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我以上都可以係一堆廢話，但最確鑿無疑的事實應該就是再對法治的服從，將會令香港民主運動受到束縛，令佢停滯不前。換言之，要真正贏，我想像到民主運動必當要正面回應這個政權下的有問題的法律制度。"},{"pid":"80ca0ee7f2459d13f9b440574855c174951bc4ec","tid":1778071,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"sorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"85db3ebb3dfb2729effcc4081f5c08ea38879869","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"739cb37db019f9504d31f8fea28f173b9332d570","tid":1778071,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"錯 香港人太善良<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/35RcTVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F35RcTVr.jpg&h=deeb3702&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5137455e14292e0f31390cce464f47cadf54d5d6","tid":1778071,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"巴士底監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba28221f8c92a10dbba531e543094fc9ca0115d","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380df852e22a94ba2dd27fd0b14fc7a03bb9f10c","tid":1778071,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"岩呀"},{"pid":"953aa061152a2df2f7864cc122a559518e0fdc8b","tid":1778071,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"exac7tly 就係鄭立講嘅嘢，盲信法律喺香港係一種宗教信仰，重要係邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8463750cf85263a13cd96aaaa57548382343b13","tid":1778071,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5137455e14292e0f31390cce464f47cadf54d5d6","tid":1778071,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"巴士底監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"呢個要睇下大家既覺悟去到幾高"},{"pid":"62295f01cc6499e0bf83a74e11ced55c429db316","tid":1778071,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953aa061152a2df2f7864cc122a559518e0fdc8b","tid":1778071,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"exac7tly 就係鄭立講嘅嘢，盲信法律喺香港係一種宗教信仰，重要係邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"有一大班法律界既人同你講法治未死先係最可悲"},{"pid":"db97674087fb4487aed5479fa53ea164f815e12c","tid":1778071,"uid":75391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62295f01cc6499e0bf83a74e11ced55c429db316","tid":1778071,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"953aa061152a2df2f7864cc122a559518e0fdc8b","tid":1778071,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"exac7tly 就係鄭立講嘅嘢，盲信法律喺香港係一種宗教信仰，重要係邪教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"有一大班法律界既人同你講法治未死先係最可悲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:19:02.000Z","msg":"緊係啦，佢地畀人告有駱應淦幫佢打，你庶民一個，返屋企打飛機啦！<br />\n<br />\n一個唔好彩入左去坐，公民黨班政棍咪多個政治光環囉，屌！"},{"pid":"0345354df2f82d86e8c6c4a4c130e921c144dcaa","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"香港尷尬嘅位係所謂仲有司法獨立，即是話法官需按其專業判被告，不受政權唆擺而彰顯法治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比大陸，大陸法官同中共權力核心本為一體，批判中國法治制度就相對明顯，要推翻呢個制度相信無太大爭議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係，手足行動之意出於公義、公利，我理解佢地道德上無做錯，二在實際操作上，縱使要強加罪名在手足身上，律政司政治打壓，以不合理罪名檢控，這個是實際法律制度操作上的重大問題。然後，法官處於被動，只能受到案件就按章辦事。呢個意義下，司法機關在不情不願之下成為政權幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁為保司法獨立，我地還應否推翻這個法律制度，我相信係將來2047之前再有手足入獄下要反思的逼切問題。"},{"pid":"e980350ac849b14f0c95e03e399b8aa7f76e45e4","tid":1778071,"uid":158980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"正返視聽 係對法律既遵從<br />\n法治同法律係一個極權社會好大分別"},{"pid":"b5dde6d5a12c9a3bda0fa2da8247993a027e957b","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"求討論<br />\n想聽大家點諗呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61119eda92d606150d7583b16ecbf038a8e6284f","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"自推 5下<br />\n無就沉底<br />\n1"},{"pid":"6747146e44ea642e2e6c29846a140090c41c8d20","tid":1778071,"uid":235588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f874b335c614